task.summary: Board now tests to make sure a ship is not placed on another ship.
Fixed bug where a ship won't be placed if any of it's nodes were on the edge of the board.
Updated InteliiJ files and created a rotation method and rotation tester in Board.
Small changes and made HeadSpots display H to tell where the head of a ship is.
Made Board abstact and added 2 Board classes.
Sunk method finished. Ship is now the parent of Hull and HeadSpot.
